<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            color: #333;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }

        .header {
            background-color: #4A90E2;
            color: white;
            padding: 24px;
            border-radius: 8px 8px 0 0;
        }

        .body {
            padding: 24px;
            background: #f9f9f9;
        }

        .detail {
            margin: 8px 0;
        }

        .label {
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #555;
        }

        .footer {
            padding: 16px 24px;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #999;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .badge {
            display: inline-block;
            background: #e8f5e9;
            color: #2e7d32;
            padding: 4px 12px;
            border-radius: 12px;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="header">
        <h2>Booking Confirmed ✓</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="body">
        <p>Hi <strong>{{UserName}}</strong>,</p>
        <p>Your booking has been successfully created. Here are the details:</p>

        <div class="detail"><span class="label">Coworking:</span> {{CoworkingName}}</div>
        <div class="detail"><span class="label">Desk:</span> {{DeskName}}</div>
        <div class="detail"><span class="label">Date:</span> {{Start}}</div>
        <div class="detail"><span class="label">From:</span> {{FormattedStart}} — {{FormattedEnd}}</div>
        <div class="detail"><span class="label">Timezone:</span> {{TimeZoneId}}</div>

        <br>
        <span class="badge">✓ Confirmed</span>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
        You received this email because a booking was made with your email address.<br>
        If this wasn't you, please contact support.
    </div>
</body>
</html>